*.svg
*.ico

# Installer wizard assets — ship in public release (re-include after blanket image ignore above)
!PAI/PAI-Install/public/assets/*.png
!PAI/PAI-Install/public/assets/*.jpg
!PAI/PAI-Install/public/assets/*.jpeg
!PAI/PAI-Install/public/assets/*.gif
!PAI/PAI-Install/public/assets/*.webp
!PAI/PAI-Install/public/assets/*.svg
!PAI/PAI-Install/public/assets/*.ico

# Pulse menu-bar icons — ship in public release
!PAI/PULSE/MenuBar/*.png
!PAI/PULSE/MenuBar/*.jpg
!PAI/PULSE/MenuBar/*.svg
!PAI/PULSE/MenuBar/*.ico

# Pulse Observability built dashboard — ship in public release so fresh installs
# get a working dashboard immediately (no `bun run build` step required).
# Broad un-ignore covers the entire built tree including pai-logo.png at root.
!PAI/PULSE/Observability/out/**

# Pulse Observability lockfile — ship for reproducible installs
!PAI/PULSE/Observability/bun.lock

